<h2 class="title"><a href="https://www.odditycentral.com/travel/tree-of-life-grows-on-salt-island-in-the-middle-of-the-dead-sea.html" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to &#8220;Tree of Life&#8221; Grows on Salt Island in the Middle of the Dead Sea">&#8220;Tree of Life&#8221; Grows on Salt Island in the Middle of the Dead Sea</a></h2>
